This paper proposes a new policy gradient estimator for continuous control tasks with bounded action spaces. As such, it is likely to be relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), control systems (cs.SY), and computer vision (cs.CV). However, given that the paper focuses on reinforcement learning and policy optimization, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely sub-categories.
